7.30	Brahma_Sarovar	Brahma Sarovar	Brahma Sarovar is a water tank sacred to the Dharmic religions in Thanesar, in the state of Haryana in North India. Dharmic religions lay emphasis on taking bath for internal and external purity. Most religious sites have water tanks or sarovar in or near the temple/gurdwara.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/0/0e/Brahma_Sarovar.jpg/240px-Brahma_Sarovar.jpg
